headline: KLA Corporation (KLAC): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: What a time it’s been for KLA Corporation. In the past six months alone, the company’s stock price has increased by a massive 43.8%, reaching $1,222 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
